<HEADLINE> 6 Injured at Nev. Carnival Accident  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   RENO, Nev. (AP) -- High winds rushed through a carnival outside
the Reno Hilton and sent a tent canopy into the air. Six people
were injured, one seriously.
</P>
